---
title: Quick Beef & Leek Fusilli with Tomato Sauce & Garlic-Parmesan Pangrattato
description: In this dish, we've teamed a rich tomato-based sauce with leek and tender beef mince for a speedy weeknight meal that looks
and smells every bit as good as it tastes.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/beef-leek-fusilli-2d2af2c5.jpg
